<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78817ec8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s715"><num value="715">§ 715.</num><heading> Short title</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall be known by the short title of “Migratory Bird Conservation Act.”</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78817ec9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1929-02-18/ch257/s1">Feb. 18, 1929, ch. 257, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/1222">45 Stat. 1222</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id78817eca-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id78817ecb-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitleOfAmendment" id="id78817ecc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title of 1976 Amendment</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/94/215/s1">Pub. L. 94–215, § 1</ref>, Feb 17, 1976, <ref href="/us/stat/90/189">90 Stat. 189</ref>, provided: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/94/215/s1">“That this Act [amending sections 668dd, 715a, 715k–3, 715k–5, 718a, 718b, and 718d of this title] may be cited as the ‘Wetlands Loan Extension Act of 1976’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
